  <entry>
    <title>安装hexo-next-search插件</title>
    <url>/blog/2020/04/24/hexo-next-search%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%8A%96%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>hexo-generator-searchdb实现本地搜索功能。安装后发现，点击搜索按钮弹出的modal框会导致页面抖动，之前学习bootstrap时候也遇到了同样的问题，顺便解决一下。</p>
<h3 id="安装hexo-generator-searchdb"><a href="#安装hexo-generator-searchdb" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo-generator-searchdb"></a>安装hexo-generator-searchdb</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="修改主题配置"><a href="#修改主题配置" class="headerlink" title="修改主题配置"></a>修改主题配置</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#./themes/next/_config.yml</span></span><br><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="修改hexo配置"><a href="#修改hexo配置" class="headerlink" title="修改hexo配置"></a>修改hexo配置</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#./_config.yml 在末尾添加下列内容</span></span><br><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  path: search.xml   <span class="comment">#在public目录的根目录下生成search.xml 文件，用于存储网站文章的文字数据.</span></span><br><span class="line">  field: post</span><br><span class="line">  format: html</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">limit</span>: 10000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="解决点击页面search抖动问题"><a href="#解决点击页面search抖动问题" class="headerlink" title="解决点击页面search抖动问题"></a>解决点击页面search抖动问题</h3><h4 id="新建-modal-styl文件"><a href="#新建-modal-styl文件" class="headerlink" title="新建_modal.styl文件"></a>新建_modal.styl文件</h4><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* /theme/next/source/css/_modal.styl */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*防止modal抖动*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">body</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="attribute">overflow</span>: auto <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.modal</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="attribute">overflow</span>: auto <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="修改main-styl文件"><a href="#修改main-styl文件" class="headerlink" title="修改main.styl文件"></a>修改main.styl文件</h4><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* /theme/next/source/css/main.styl */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 文末添加 _modal.styl文件</span></span><br><span class="line">@import "_modal.styl";</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>前端</category>
      </categories>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>hexo首页显示文章摘要和阅读全文</title>
    <url>/blog/2020/04/27/hexo%E9%A6%96%E9%A1%B5%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81%E5%92%8C%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%E5%85%A8%E6%96%87/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="在博客根目录下执行"><a href="#在博客根目录下执行" class="headerlink" title="在博客根目录下执行"></a>在博客根目录下执行</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-excerpt --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="修改-config-yml配置文件"><a href="#修改-config-yml配置文件" class="headerlink" title="修改_config.yml配置文件"></a>修改_config.yml配置文件</h2><h3 id="excerpt-description-改为true"><a href="#excerpt-description-改为true" class="headerlink" title="excerpt_description 改为true"></a>excerpt_description 改为true</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Automatically excerpt description in homepage as preamble text.</span></span><br><span class="line">excerpt_description: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">### 在配置文件_config.yml添加</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96; bash</span><br><span class="line"># _config.yml</span><br><span class="line">  excerpt:</span><br><span class="line">    depth: 10</span><br><span class="line">    excerpt_excludes: []</span><br><span class="line">    more_excludes: []</span><br><span class="line">    hideWholePostExcerpts: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>前端</category>
      </categories>
